<h2 style="margin-top:0;color:#111827;">Reset Your Password</h2>
<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;">
  Hi {{firstName}}, we received a request to reset your password. Use the code below to proceed.
</p>

<div style="margin:28px 0;text-align:center;">
  <div style="display:inline-block;background:#fff7ed;border:1px dashed #fed7aa;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 32px;">
    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;">Reset Code</p>
    <p style="margin:0;font-size:36px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:8px;color:#111827;">{{resetCode}}</p>
  </div>
  <p style="margin:10px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;">This code expires in {{expiresIn}}.</p>
</div>

<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;">
  If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will not change.
</p>
